==Steps==
# Talk to Natasha
# Meet Natasha in the Overworld
# Go to the Eversummer Florist
# Talk to Vaska and buy a flower bouquet
# Talk to Natasha
# Go to the place where Natasha and her adoptive parents are meeting
# Search for clues left by Vache in the Snow Plains
# Continue searching for clues in the Snow Plains
# Investigate the abandoned lab
# Fulfill Natasha's last request
# Talk to Natasha

